Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.46,0:01:46.25,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur6}现在将其点燃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:53.84,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur6}焦躁不安  渴求着更多
