Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:02:00.02,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur6}感受这炽热
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:04.15,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur6}撩动感官  刺激的浪漫
